message.content: cs.IT, cs.IT is the most likely category as the paper deals with information theory and entropy. Other possible categories could be cs.DS (data structures and algorithms) as the paper involves mathematical inequalities and optimization, cs.SI (social and information networks) as entropy power is a concept used in network information theory, cs.LG (machine learning) as entropy is a commonly used measure in machine learning, and cs.NA (numerical analysis) as the paper involves optimization techniques.
